{
  "id": "69b7978e2ccf018b38a06632",
  "title": "子音",
  "created": 1773639576,
  "updated": 1773645618,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b7978e2ccf018b38a06632",
      "text": "子音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639576,
      "updated": 1773642087
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79797000000000033063f",
      "text": "広く使われる言語において殆どの子音は、子音は肺から空気を送り調音される",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639576,
      "updated": 1773639634
    },
    {
      "id": "69b797d30000000000330641",
      "text": "\t[非肺臓気流音]を聞くほうが肺臓気流音について理解するのが容易くなる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639636,
      "updated": 1773639661
    },
    {
      "id": "69b797f40000000000330642",
      "text": "\t\t異なるものを見て初めてアクロニム的に名前の必要性がわかるのだ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639669,
      "updated": 1773639690
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7980b0000000000330643",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639692,
      "updated": 1773639692
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7980b0000000000330644",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639692,
      "updated": 1773639692
    },
    {
      "id": "69b797a00000000000330640",
      "text": "table:子音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639585,
      "updated": 1773640786
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79c520000000000551e2d",
      "text": " 肺臓気流音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640786,
      "updated": 1773640789
    },
    {
      "id": "69b798dd000000000033066c",
      "text": " \t両唇\t唇歯\t歯\t歯茎\tそり舌\t硬口蓋\t軟口蓋\t口蓋垂\t咽頭\t声門",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639902,
      "updated": 1773641147
    },
    {
      "id": "69b798260000000000330647",
      "text": " 無声破裂\tp\t(p̪)\t(t̪)\tt\tʈ\tc\tk\tq\t(ʡˤ)\tʔ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773645513
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79833000000000033064f",
      "text": " 有声破裂\tb\t(b̪)\t(d̪)\td\tɖ\tɟ\tɡ\tɢ\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639732,
      "updated": 1773641146
    },
    {
      "id": "69b798260000000000330648",
      "text": " 無声鼻音\t(m̥)\t(ɱ̊)\t(n̪̊)\t(n̥)\t\t\t\t\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7999d000000000033066d",
      "text": " 有声鼻音\tm\tɱ\t(n̪)\tn\tɳ\tɲ\tŋ\tɴ\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640094,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b798260000000000330649",
      "text": " 無声震え\t(ʙ̥)\t\t(r̥)\t(r̥)\t\t\t✕\tʀ\tʀ\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79a830000000000551de7",
      "text": " 有声震え\tʙ\t\tr\tr\t\t\t✕\tʀ\tʀ\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640323,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79826000000000033064a",
      "text": " 有声弾き\t(ⱱ̟)\tⱱ\tɾ\tɾ\tɽ\t(ɟ̆)\t✕\t(ɢ̆)\t(ʡ̆)\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79826000000000033064b",
      "text": " 無声摩擦\tɸ\tf\tθ\ts / ʃ\tʂ\tɕ / ç\tx\tχ\tħ\th\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641464
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79b1e0000000000551df2",
      "text": " 有声摩擦\tβ\tv\tð\tz / ʒ\tʐ\tʑ / ʝ\tɣ\tʁ\tʕ\tɦ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640479,
      "updated": 1773641468
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79e1c0000000000551e3c",
      "text": " 無声破擦\tp͡ɸ\tp̪͡f\tt͡θ\tt͡s / t͡ʃ\tʈ͡ʂ\tt͡ɕ / c͡ç\tk͡x\tq͡χ\tt͡ɬ\tʔ͡h\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641244,
      "updated": 1773645604
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79e230000000000551e3d",
      "text": " 有声破擦\tb͡β\tb̪͡v\td͡ð\td͡z / d͡ʒ\tɖ͡ʐ\td͡ʑ / ɟ͡ʝ\tɡ͡ɣ\tɢ͡ʁ\td͡ɮ\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641251,
      "updated": 1773645605
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79826000000000033064c",
      "text": " 無声側面摩擦\t✕\t✕\tɬ\tɬ\t\t\t\t\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641176
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79bb20000000000551e21",
      "text": " 有声側面摩擦\t✕\t✕\tɮ\tɮ\t\t\t\t\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640626,
      "updated": 1773641181
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79826000000000033064d",
      "text": " 無声接近\t\t(ʋ̥)\t(ɹ̥)\t(ɹ̥)\t\t\t\t\t\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79826000000000033064e",
      "text": " 有声接近\t(β̞)\tʋ\tɹ\tɹ\tɻ\tj\tɰ\t\t\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773639719,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79bf50000000000551e22",
      "text": " 無声側面接近\t✕\t✕\t(l̥)\t(l̥)\t\t\t\t\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640693,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79c760000000000551e2e",
      "text": " 有声側面接近\t✕\t✕\tl\tl\tɭ\tʎ\tʟ\t\t✕\t✕",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640823,
      "updated": 1773641145
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7981f0000000000330645",
      "text": "\t非肺臓気流音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641140,
      "updated": 1773641896
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0b20000000000551e6e",
      "text": "  吸着\tʘ\t\tǀ\tǃ\t!! (!̢ )\tǂ\t(ʞ)\t(ʞ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641907,
      "updated": 1773642151
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0b30000000000551e71",
      "text": "  側面吸着\t\t\t\tǁ\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641908,
      "updated": 1773642152
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0b30000000000551e72",
      "text": "  入破\tɓ\t\tɗ̪\tɗ\t(ᶑ)\tʄ\tɠ\tʛ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641908,
      "updated": 1773645616
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0b30000000000551e73",
      "text": "  放出\tpʼ\t\t(t̪ʼ)\ttʼ\tʈʼ\tcʼ\tkʼ\t(qʼ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641908,
      "updated": 1773645617
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0b30000000000551e74",
      "text": "  摩擦放出\t\t\t\tsʼ\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641908,
      "updated": 1773645618
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0a30000000000551e6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641892,
      "updated": 1773641892
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79ce50000000000551e37",
      "text": " s / ʃ 、z / ʒ は歯茎音と後部歯茎音の違い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640934,
      "updated": 1773641158
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79f3f0000000000551e6c",
      "text": " ɕ / ç、ʑ / ʝ は歯茎硬口蓋音と歯茎音の違い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641536,
      "updated": 1773641570
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79dcd0000000000551e38",
      "text": " ✕は調音不可能と考えられているもの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641166,
      "updated": 1773641190
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a0ed0000000000551e76",
      "text": " \t空欄は検討もされていないものだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641965,
      "updated": 1773641978
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79de60000000000551e39",
      "text": " 丸括弧は [https://www.internationalphoneticassociation.org/content/ipa-chart IPA子音表 (2005)] に記載されていないもの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641190,
      "updated": 1773641225
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79dee0000000000551e3a",
      "text": " この表に載っていない子音がまだある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773641199,
      "updated": 1773643018
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a6520000000000551e96",
      "text": "  有気音・無気音の対立",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643346,
      "updated": 1773643376
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a6620000000000551e97",
      "text": "  \t有声音・無声音の他に有気音・無気音の対立がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643363,
      "updated": 1773643402
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a67c0000000000551e98",
      "text": "  \tしかも、有声音・無声音の対立と有気音・無気音の対立が同時に成立する言語がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643388,
      "updated": 1773643428
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a5490000000000551e90",
      "text": " \ttable:喉頭蓋音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643082,
      "updated": 1773643113
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a56f0000000000551e91",
      "text": " \t 無声摩擦音\t有声摩擦音\t喉頭蓋破裂音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643119,
      "updated": 1773643179
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a57f0000000000551e92",
      "text": " \t ʜ\tʢ\tʡ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643136,
      "updated": 1773643180
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a5b10000000000551e93",
      "text": " \ttable:舌唇音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643186,
      "updated": 1773643225
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a5e20000000000551e95",
      "text": " \t 無声破裂音\t有声破裂音\t無声鼻音\t無声摩擦音\t有声摩擦音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643234,
      "updated": 1773643283
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a5d90000000000551e94",
      "text": " \t (t̼)\t(d̼)\t(n̼)\t(θ̼)\t(ð̼)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643225,
      "updated": 1773643234
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a1ce0000000000551e77",
      "text": " \ttable:同時調音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642191,
      "updated": 1773642227
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a1d70000000000551e78",
      "text": " \t\t\t両唇軟口蓋\t両唇硬口蓋\t歯茎硬口蓋\t「謎」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642199,
      "updated": 1773643028
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a21b0000000000551e7d",
      "text": "   破裂\t(k͡p)\t(ɡ͡b)\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642268,
      "updated": 1773642392
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a2550000000000551e82",
      "text": "   鼻\t\t(ŋ͡m)\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642325,
      "updated": 1773642393
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a1f50000000000551e7a",
      "text": " \t\t摩擦\tʍ\t\tɕ / ʑ\tɧ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642229,
      "updated": 1773642400
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a1df0000000000551e79",
      "text": "   接近\tw\tɥ\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642207,
      "updated": 1773642397
    },
    {
      "id": "69b79b780000000000551e1f",
      "text": "  ɧ はスウェーデン語で正書法上 sj と綴られる発音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773640569,
      "updated": 1773642532
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a32e0000000000551e86",
      "text": "  \tスウェーデン語の話者にとっては珍しい音ではないが、この音がどのように調音されているかは、音声学者の記述がかならずしも一致しない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642543,
      "updated": 1773642552
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a33a0000000000551e88",
      "text": "  \t1. 国際音声学会ではこの音を「後部歯茎 /ʃ/ と軟口蓋 /x/ の同時調音」(simultaneous ʃ and x) としているが、2か所で摩擦が起きるというのは不自然であり、実際にこのような調音がされることがあるとは考えにくい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642554,
      "updated": 1773642663
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a3a70000000000551e89",
      "text": "  \t2. 実際の発音は地理的および社会的方言によって異なる。ピーター・ラディフォギッドとイアン・マディソンによる Per Lindblad の記述の再解釈によると、/ɧ/ は実際には以下のふた通りの発音がよく現れるという。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642664,
      "updated": 1773642691
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a3c80000000000551e8e",
      "text": "    軟口蓋化 /x/ した無声唇歯摩擦音 /f/ で、さらに円唇性 (例: ü 等) をもち、上唇は突きだしている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642697,
      "updated": 1773642943
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a3a90000000000551e8c",
      "text": "    無声軟口蓋摩擦音 /x/ だが、/x/ にくらべて摩擦が弱く、かつ少し前寄りかもしれない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642665,
      "updated": 1773642969
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a3040000000000551e85",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773642501,
      "updated": 1773642501
    }
  ]
}